# Paper zip artifact

Whenever you edit, rebuild, commit, or push this paper repo, **always create or refresh `paper.zip` at the repo root**.

## Contents

Include the submission-ready paper files (not LaTeX aux junk):

- `paper/agents-unite-paper.tex`
- `paper/agents-unite-paper.pdf`
- `paper/references.bib`

## How

Prefer the Makefile target:

```bash
make zip
```

On Windows PowerShell if `make` is unavailable:

```powershell
Compress-Archive -Path paper/agents-unite-paper.tex,paper/agents-unite-paper.pdf,paper/references.bib -DestinationPath paper.zip -Force
```

## When

- After rebuilding the PDF
- Before committing or pushing paper changes
- At the end of any session that touched `paper/*`

Do not leave a stale `paper.zip` after source/PDF updates.
